import { BrowserRouter, NavLink, Route, Routes } from "react-router-dom"

const DialogsRoute = ()=> {
    return <Routes>
        <Route path="/dialogs/first" element={<Dialog message='first' />} />
        <Route path="/dialogs/second" element={<Dialog message='second' />} />
        <Route path="/dialogs/third" element={<Dialog message='third' />} />
    </Routes>
}

export default DialogsRoute
